                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5150" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0064</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9797 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“保险+期货”到“订单+保险+期货”——大商所的农业风险管理新途径</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Insurance + Futures&quot; to &quot;Order + Insurance + Futures&quot;-DCE&#39;s New Approach to Agricultural Risk Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安辉，何萱，齐晓东</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连商品交易所</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连商品交易所；“订单+保险+期货”；收入保障；成本收益</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dalian Commodity Exchange ,“ Order + Insurance + Futures”， Income Security , Cost Benefit</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">摘 要：为应对2016年玉米收储政策取消带来的农产品价格风险，2017年10月，大连商品交易所响应中央一号文件，在原有的“保险+期货”基础上，探索“订单+保险+期货”的新模式，成功保障了农民的售粮渠道，并为农民收益提供双保险。本案例以从“保险+期货”的一般模式到“订单+保险+期货”创新模式的发展进程为脉络，梳理了大商所吉林云天化玉米价格险试点项目的运作流程，分析各参与方的合作方式及成本收益情况，是研究金融衍生品创新解决农业风险的典型案例。通过案例的学习，学生可以掌握成本收益分析方法，理解“订单+保险+期货”这一新模式的原理及策略选择。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abstract: In order to solve the price risk brought by the transformation of Chinese farm products into a market-based acquisition mode in 2016, in October 2017, The Central Document No. 1 proposed to explore the “Order + Insurance + Futures” model based on the “Insurance + Futures” model, and this new mode has successfully secured farmers &#39;food sales channels and provided double insurance for farmers&#39; income. This case is based on the development process from the general model of &quot;insurance + futures&quot; to the innovative model of &quot;order + insurance + futures&quot;, and analyses the cooperation method as well as the costs and benefits of each of the project’s cooperatives through the operation process of Jilin Yuntianhua corn price insurance pilot project of Dalian Commodity Exchange(DCE). As a typical case about the innovation of financial derivatives to solve agricultural risks, students can master the cost-benefit analysis method and understand the operation of the new model of “order + insurance + futures” through the study of it.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《期权、期货及其他衍生产品》、《公司金融》、《保险学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险、订单农业、保险、期货；农产品期货价格保险运作机制；“订单+保险+期货”模式评价；对冲策略、成本收益分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-02</td>
                            </tr>
